<c74object name='sp.waveguidemesh~' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Physical model of a vibrating membrame</digest>
    <description>Physical model of a vibrating membrame.</description>
    <discussion>    <h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
    <p>The <o>sp.waveguidemesh~</o> object is an implementation of Digital Waveguide Meshes to model vibrating membranes. This is a 3 nodes triangular Digital Waveguide Mesh model (each node consist of 6 waveguides) implemented with a few other options like damping and nonlinearity.</p>
</discussion>

